::KitKat::

She was running after Bobertron, and then had shots fired at her from the 
air.  She jumped, side stepped and twisted around trying to dodge the hail 
of bullets being sent her way.  She went after Bobertron who was carrying 
Cheetor.  A bullet hit in the tail.  She let out a yelp.
"HEY, WATCH OUT WHERE YOUR FIRING THAT THING, YOU CAN KILL SOMEONE YOU 
KNOW!" she yelled at the flying bot.  She kept after Bobertron.
"GIVE US BACK OUR BOT!" she yelled at Bobertron.
Her hip hurt from the previous fight, but she ignored the pain and kept 
running.
